                </div>
                
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h3>İzleme Platformları</h3>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="https://www.crunchyroll.com" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i> Crunchyroll</a></li>
